---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Approach" description="Monachil's proprietary platform is focused on downside protection and generating attractive risk-adjusted returns.">

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="page-hero-breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / Approach</p>
    <h1>Our <strong>Approach</strong></h1>
    <p class="page-hero-sub">Monachil's proprietary platform is focused on downside protection and generating attractive risk-adjusted returns.</p>
    <div class="page-hero-rule"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--centered">
      <p class="section-label">Investment Verticals</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Specialty Finance <strong>Focus</strong></h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto">Lending against loans, receivables, and contractual cash flows across complementary asset-backed verticals.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="cards-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Secured Consumer Finance</h3>
        <p class="card-excerpt">Auto loans, leases, device loans, and home improvement loans through high-growth specialty finance originators.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Unsecured Consumer Finance</h3>
        <p class="card-excerpt">Personal installment loans, specialty student lending, and point-of-sale financing with strong borrower alignment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">SME Credit</h3>
        <p class="card-excerpt">Merchant cash advance, small-business lines of credit, and working capital financing for established borrowers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="12 2 2 7 12 12 22 7 12 2"/><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"/><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Other Specialty Finance</h3>
        <p class="card-excerpt">Factoring and invoice finance, asset-based lending, and other specialty lending verticals with predictable cash flows.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="card-title">Monachil Credit Income Fund</h3>
        <p class="card-excerpt">Registered, continuously offered closed-end interval fund providing access to Monachil's private credit strategy.</p>
        <a href="https://monachilfunds.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="card-link card-link--inline">Learn More &nearr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--sky fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="who-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="section-header">
          <p class="section-label">Investment Philosophy</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Downside protection first. <strong>Returns follow.</strong></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="who-text">
          <p>The firm strives to underwrite with a <strong>capital preservation-first mandate</strong> on all investments with downside protection, control, and transparency as the foundation.</p>
          <p>The firm is most proud of its risk management framework, which focuses on retaining the <strong>"V" in LTV</strong> while delivering attractive risk-adjusted returns. Prioritizing diversity of investments by industry, product and geography, strict covenants, data analytics, and sizing deals in the $5&ndash;30mm range helps drive performance and mitigate risk.</p>
          <p>Monachil brings a <strong>creative and flexible approach</strong> to investment solutions across numerous verticals with control, transparency and downside protection as the foundation.</p>
          <blockquote class="pull-quote">We focus on retaining the <strong>"V" in LTV</strong> — ensuring the value backing every loan is monitored, verified, and protected.</blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pillars">
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <p class="pillar-title">Senior Secured Positioning</p>
            <p class="pillar-desc">First-lien seniority in the capital stack with strong security packages and covenants for downside mitigation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <p class="pillar-title">Real-Time Monitoring</p>
            <p class="pillar-desc">Proprietary risk platform consumes source data, reconciles portfolio-level information, and provides daily asset performance reporting.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <p class="pillar-title">Diversification</p>
            <p class="pillar-desc">Diversity across industry, product, and geography with deal sizing in the $5&ndash;30mm range to manage concentration risk.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <p class="pillar-title">Borrower Alignment</p>
            <p class="pillar-desc">Originators retain material first-loss exposure, ensuring alignment of interest and skin in the game.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pillar">
          <div class="pillar-icon"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg></div>
          <div>
            <p class="pillar-title">Data-Driven Decisions</p>
            <p class="pillar-desc">Real-time analytics integral to deal-level and portfolio risk management across the investment lifecycle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="inline-disclaimer">Past performance is not indicative of future results. All investments involve risk, including possible loss of principal.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <p class="section-label">Investment Process</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Differentiated, <strong>Data-Driven</strong> Investment Process</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">A transparent, disciplined and repeatable investment process with proven ability to add value through various market cycles.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num-col"><span class="step-num">01</span></div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <p class="step-title">Origination</p>
          <p class="step-desc">Monachil sources and reviews investment opportunities from multiple sourcing channels, leveraging a dedicated sourcing team and deep industry relationships.</p>
          <ul class="step-bullets">
            <li>Direct relationships with borrowers and origination partners</li>
            <li>Focus on originators with strong business models and recurring cash flows</li>
            <li>Market dislocation opportunities identified through proprietary screening</li>
            <li>Rigorous initial review with investment committee input</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num-col"><span class="step-num">02</span></div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <p class="step-title">Underwriting</p>
          <p class="step-desc">The underwriting process includes structuring, rigorous due diligence and quantitative analysis on asset performance and cash flows.</p>
          <ul class="step-bullets">
            <li>Key terms discussion with focus on collateral analysis and loan-to-value</li>
            <li>Originators retain material first-loss exposure</li>
            <li>First-lien seniority positioning in the capital stack</li>
            <li>Strong security packages and covenants for downside mitigation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num-col"><span class="step-num">03</span></div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <p class="step-title">Execution</p>
          <p class="step-desc">All investments are reviewed by the investment committee and approved by the CIO.</p>
          <ul class="step-bullets">
            <li>Funding schedules aligned with borrower growth trajectories</li>
            <li>Structural protections enforcing agreement compliance</li>
            <li>Outside counsel engaged in drafting and closing all transactions</li>
            <li>Clear terms with enforceable covenants</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num-col"><span class="step-num">04</span></div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <p class="step-title">Monitoring</p>
          <p class="step-desc">Real-time surveillance of any deviation from expectations with dedicated data analytics capabilities.</p>
          <ul class="step-bullets">
            <li>Dedicated Data Analytics team for asset-level portfolio surveillance</li>
            <li>Bespoke reporting for contractual term supervision</li>
            <li>Ongoing covenant compliance monitoring</li>
            <li>Daily asset performance reporting through proprietary risk platform</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num-col"><span class="step-num">05</span></div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <p class="step-title">Portfolio Management</p>
          <p class="step-desc">Each fund is managed according to its investment objectives with tactical flexibility and comprehensive controls.</p>
          <ul class="step-bullets">
            <li>Tactical capital allocation flexibility across opportunities</li>
            <li>Currency hedging where appropriate</li>
            <li>Monachil maintains complete control of funding accounts</li>
            <li>Disciplined capital allocation procedures</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--centered">
      <h2 class="section-title">Ready to <strong>learn more</strong>?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto">We welcome the opportunity to discuss how Monachil can fit within your portfolio.</p>
      <div class="section-cta">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
